quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  56,75,Mi woondirii mutir…óe koode …óen
  56,76,"Pellet, …óum ko woondoore mawnde, si hi…óon anndunoo"
  56,77,Pellet ndee ko Alqur'aanaare konde teddunde
  56,78,wonnde e deftere reenaande
  56,79,meemataa nden si wanaa la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďen
  56,80,ko jippiniraande ka Jey…óo Winndere nden
  56,81,E ko ndee yewtere wonki ko pennoton onon
  56,82,"Hi…óon wa…óa arsike mon (to…ďo ngon) ko on fennoo…ďe [arsiku…óo On]"
  56,83,Ko ha…óata nde wonkii yottii ka looko∆īere
  56,84,hara onon hi…óon ndaara ontuma
  56,85,"hara non ko Menen …ďuri on …ďadaade mo, kono on yi'ataa"
  56,86,"Ko ha…óata on, si tawiino hara on warjetaake"
  56,87,"rutton kin [wonkii], si tawii ko on goongu…ďe"
  56,88,Si tawii on ko jeyaa…óo e …ďattinaa…ďe …ďen
  56,89,"haray ko fowtere, e mo∆ī∆īere, e Aljannaaji neema (woodani mo)"
  56,90,Si tawii kadi ko jeyaa…óo e yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďen
  56,91,"haray [o ja…ď…ďoroyte] : \"Kisal maa\" e …ďaŇčge yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďen"
  56,92,Si tawii non ko jeyanoo…óo e fennu…ďe majju…ďe …ďen
  56,93,haray ho…ótorde makko on ko fatay…óam
  56,94,e sumeede Jahiimi
  56,95,"Pellet, ko …óum woni goonga yananaa…óo on"
  56,96,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, Maw…óo On"